Dossier_Bilan_S29.TEXT: You are about to submit parameters for the Dossier Bilan Professionnelle. The platform will generate Task and notification for student to upload Certification Passport (if you select this option). Are you sure ?

Dossier_Bilan_S31.TEXT: Changes cannot be saved as this Dossier Bilan has already been marked as 'Finished'. No further modifications are permitted.

Dossier_Bilan_S32.TITLE: Submission Not Allowed
Dossier_Bilan_S32.TEXT: The parameters cannot be submitted again as the status of this Dossier Bilan is already marked as 'Finished'. No further modifications are allowed.

Dossier_Bilan_S33.TEXT: A Dossier Bilan cannot be created for this class and title because there are no students enrolled. Please ensure at least one student is added to proceed.

Dossier_Bilan_S34.TITLE: Duplicate Name Detected
Dossier_Bilan_S34.TEXT: Dossier Bilan with this name already exists. Please choose a different name to proceed.

Dossier_Bilan_S35.TEXT: The 'Include Job Description' option cannot be activated because it is currently disabled in the class parameters. Please enable job description processing in the class settings first.
